research_municipality_step.notes: Brownfield, TX operates under a Council-Manager form of government with a mayor and two at-large council members, and five district council members. Eric Horton became Mayor in May 2024. Mary Valdonado won the election for District 2 Council Member in May 2024. Lee Gamez won the election for District 3 Council Member in May 2024. There was conflicting information regarding the Mayor Pro Tem role and some council member names/districts across different sources; the official city website and recent election results were prioritized for accuracy.
